Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还像金鱼粪一样粘着阿扁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我跟田村老婆婆问好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.75,0:00:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是海王的先锋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法能把月本君拉到我们队么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会输的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是不打
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间学长在哪里
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:11.63,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新しい時代が来たのに煮詰まって抜け出せない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:17.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この道が真っ直ぐ過ぎて逃げれもしない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～選ぶにも道がなくて 迷走中！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:23.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何がしたいか一人わからなくて 妄想中！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.03,0:01:28.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自分と他人を比べて お～ちてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:35.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,オイラ世界にたった一人だよ いつも世界にたった一人だヨ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,でもやるのだーの！ オレにしかできないことなんてないかも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:48.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,しれな～いけど 何もしないまま消えて～ゆくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:51.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もしないまま消えて～ゆくの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:55.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もしないまま消えてゆくもんかあ～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.65,0:02:02.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何だって！ いーつだって気持ちイイことがしたいだけえ！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-a)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的决定啦？文革
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看没必要一个人勉强留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}孔文革 中国右式直拍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}高中联赛预选8强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}两面反胶旋转球攻击型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我现在回去怎么见人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且不管怎样 学校是出了钱请我来训练咱们那批傻小子的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 再见 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 说得不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一令我欣慰的是风间在世界赛上也赢得了冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子要在联赛里输了 我真找个巫婆来把他变成青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍不得你啊 文革
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间君 恭喜你获得青年奥林匹克单打冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体和双打虽然不太理想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但单打冠军让我感到满足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}风间龙一(飞龙) 右手横拍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}青年奥林匹克冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}旋转球主战近中远台全能型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我最担心的是我的母校海王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在队伍整体实力的下降显而易见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我们海王学园要想像以前那般坚如磐石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑高中的月本选手级别的选手是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 拍广告的那位？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「波塞冬」的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然时间很短
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是青年奥林匹克单打冠军风间龙一君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本报道到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打乒乓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}乒乓用品就找波塞冬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤泽站前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你 阿龙好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵美子婶婶也很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络一下啦 她会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听她说每次都要给客人看阿龙的剪报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去跟老头打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有好吃的松饼店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿龙明明都是世界第一了还这么辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像世界中心还有老头在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很便宜了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡假海滩比这里贵一倍多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有遮阳伞30分钟就会晒成焦炭的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椅子也一定要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙子全粘身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我涂防晒霜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥啊超搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕裂痕好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有家有名的松饼店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙点一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来到了海边跟水也合不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山里看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该到时间了 好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得很好 龙一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就在你身上花钱拍广告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过架子很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电视上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会来我们这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该明白自己该去什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 海王必须保持常胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 龙一 你那么说不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是明白你真的在为海王担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可联赛输得一塌糊涂的那些家伙还没振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}海王学园遭击沉 团体第二轮败退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长只关心他校选手不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}未能蝉联
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}风间龙一君 单打蝉联
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 风间是被叫出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午电视上 在机场给说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是个机器人一样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴角没上扬过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫月本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何 以风间的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会大意说漏嘴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的打算把那个三七分眼镜拉到我们这来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}佐久间学(恶魔) 右手直拍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}高中联赛第2轮败退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}反胶高吊前台攻守型
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(236,500)}哪里弄错了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢下来了哦 速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速 加速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手摆起来 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持住 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}月本诚(笑脸) 右手横拍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}联赛预选第3战败退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}两面反胶削球主战型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别停下别停下 走起来走起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 大田队长 要回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我们结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要帮忙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 总觉得不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大田 今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考执照啊执照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开我家的轻卡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家业可继啊 不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像我们这种未来一片漆黑的考生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不知道镇上的小家电商店的艰辛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天那个西瓜头也没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去吧 身子会着凉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是连续接球的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用脚步 脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧 你回的球太飘了　别只用手接
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚步乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢赤城乳业啊 个人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由的经营模式给人好感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK的广告也很有创意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰激凌系的热卖了也没有自大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续推出新产品的意欲很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全黑了啊 我还以为是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不打了吗 星野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有点胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.48,0:10:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月本在外面跟老头绕圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那家伙跟我们完全是不同的训练内容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上5点就来学校跑10公里哦10公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光运动量就是我们的3倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外比赛也是 老头发疯似的使劲安排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hello everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点胖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新买的眼镜让你看走眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.57,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零食吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的方针
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯子似的跟他校安排比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是因为队里没个人能当他的练习对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我们也得陪他跟那个级别的学校打
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子大人独自奔跑在连胜大道上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个部已经不存在团队了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一个人是主力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他都是捡球的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 佐久间不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 说是有点感冒 在宿舍静养
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 算了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐久间的感冒我是不信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是盲肠肿胀还挥着拍子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙房间里的海报我是笑不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他对你可是像神一样的崇拜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他肯定是跑什么地方去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是严禁擅自对外比赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐久间明知这点 还是出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不管你有多想要片高那个叫月本的削球手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.47,0:12:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你要老是说我们不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聚拢的人心也聚集不来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 风间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风间 休息结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想佐久间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 佐久间打的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐久间会输
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月本诚的水平与你们已经不在同一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有金桂的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长 差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 马上就去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之佐久间空出来的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出填补空位的人材是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到你这话佐久间会怎么想 啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起同甘共苦过的佐久间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问那份怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们海王乒乓部的名门复活有何用处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能上世界大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至在高中联赛里也没法取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧态依然 危急存亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒冬将至
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很不得了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是觉得好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿龙在电视上说的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个这年头很少见的1年级新生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.89,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打先锋的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有比谁脑子不开窍的大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他属于能立马入围的级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.22,0:14:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我们挖来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说他入部时我们强烈反对过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对他说你会很痛苦的 拒绝他了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是想成为风间前辈一样人才来海王的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不听劝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他以后可以当经理人就勉强收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙却是个叫他做十遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会做百遍千遍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过乒乓是个很看天分的竞技
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把龙一当目标太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过爸爸我很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得他太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的队伍也是 即使不比全盛期的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.99,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.98,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想让龙一能有同样的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如意十有八九
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短大毕业后你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还在考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喊出声音来 1年级
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.32,0:15:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 怎么了 Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么停下 come on
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你散光眼已经这么严重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞错车站了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是海王…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有点胖了吧 阿扁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了 请问监督在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 我是海王1年级的佐久间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天前来 是想和月本选手比赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打是可以打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔 你会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛我是不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的学校是禁止个人的对外比赛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 输了的话马上退部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 Mr.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像新撰组一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤勇都没许可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟土方都没告诉就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说已经有切腹的觉悟了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK Mr.冲田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的时间就稍微送点给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我15分钟结束掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的训练课程还要消化完的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次跟你打有2年4个月了啊 笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是96胜37败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事早就忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微被风间学长看中了也别给我自大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的连胜纪录也是跟只会龟缩的对手玩出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井底之蛙瞎扑腾罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1比0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是有点长进了嘛 笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住笑脸的第3球了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然海王就是不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2比0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.95,0:18:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3比0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4比0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11比1 月本胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑脸你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么单纯的旋转球别上当啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂恶魔 别打笑脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是阿扁 这家伙完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直一点进步都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2比11 月本胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 球种根本看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威慑也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不转球也照接不误
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛记分 0比2 月本发球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是在跟大学生或者社会人打球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底哪里弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是被什么绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散光很厉害啊 学君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里弄错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后眼睛累了的话就看远方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子跟我不同眼睛很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学 看看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 学 那是电车哦 不是小轿车
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里弄错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高中毕业了准备去欧洲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 佐久间是先锋啊 我很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被什么绊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.52,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从绊倒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线球 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5比0
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我努力过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的10倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 100倍 1000倍努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让风间学长认可
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了胜过阿扁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此从早到晚都只想着乒乓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了乒乓奉献了所有 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为恶魔你没有乒乓的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至于大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打算继续比赛的话请你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有那么闲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后据说李小龙的死因还有其他说法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 你走路看哪里啊小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}海王学园乒乓球部员佐久间学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走路要看哪里你才会夸我啊 啊？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因伤人事件2星期的停学处分 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回答啊 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}乒乓球部 退部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好成佛吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:39.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤い陽が僕を睨む様
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.42,0:21:46.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あくびしたら滲んだ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:53.63,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望みはメトロノームのよう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:22:00.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全てだけが終わり告げる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢ではない　そうでもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:07.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはね　ここにもない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.57,0:22:11.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かのタバコを吸って　一息ついたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光りだす俺　決意の絵文字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.61,0:22:17.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てはfade away？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知らぬ存ぜぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:21.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未だwonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:25.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨が降っても濡れないんだぜ
